spec_data.Name: python3-cairosvg
spec_data.Description:
CairoSVG is a SVG converter based on Cairo. It can export SVG files to PDF,
PostScript and PNG files.

For further information, please visit the CairoSVG Website
http://www.cairosvg.org
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 12:09:24 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A Simple SVG Converter for Cairo
